GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/stress-tested-testing-stress-novel-organoid-models-how-the-adrenal-gland-develops</guid></item><item><title>在 Mammouth 一处访问所有最好的 AI 模型</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/get-access-to-all-the-best-ai-models-in-one-place-at-mammouth</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 00:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/get-access-to-all-the-best-ai-models-in-one-place-at-mammouth</guid></item><item><title>再见，糖尿病前期，你好，2 型糖尿病阶段？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/goodbye-prediabetes-hello-type-2-diabetes-stages</link><description>“糖尿病前期”的概念可能正在被淘汰。一些专家建议改为对 2 型糖尿病进行分期，认为当前的标签可能会产生误导，并可能会延迟更积极的治疗。基于阶段的方法可以更好地反映疾病进展并鼓励早期干预。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/goodbye-prediabetes-hello-type-2-diabetes-stages2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 00:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/goodbye-prediabetes-hello-type-2-diabetes-stages</guid></item><item><title>新的“统一理论”可以解释阿尔茨海默病如何在大脑中出现</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-unifying-theory-may-explain-how-alzheimers-emerges-in-the-brain</link><description>的起源&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-unifying-theory-may-explain-how-alzheimers-emerges-in-the-brain.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 00:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-unifying-theory-may-explain-how-alzheimers-emerges-in-the-brain</guid></item><item><title>欢迎 Gemma 4：设备上的前沿多模式智能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/welcome-gemma-4-frontier-multimodal-intelligence-on-device</link><description>我们正在通过开源和开放科学推进人工智能并使之民主化。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/welcome-gemma-4-frontier-multimodal-intelligence-on-device3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 23:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/welcome-gemma-4-frontier-multimodal-intelligence-on-device</guid></item><item><title>研究表明免疫重编程可治疗念珠菌病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/study-points-toward-immune-reprogramming-to-treat-candidiasis</link><description>系统性念珠菌病是一种很难有效治疗的机会性真菌感染。研究发表在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/study-points-toward-immune-reprogramming-to-treat-candidiasis.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 23:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/study-points-toward-immune-reprogramming-to-treat-candidiasis</guid></item><item><title>癌症的衰老：标志、悖论和治疗前景</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/senescence-in-cancer-hallmarks-paradoxes-and-therapeutic-promise</link><description>现已上线！细胞衰老由六个主要特征定义，是一种停止细胞分裂，同时重新连接染色质、新陈代谢、微环境感知和免疫相互作用以抑制或促进癌症的程序，是精准治疗的一个令人兴奋的前沿领域。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/senescence-in-cancer-hallmarks-paradoxes-and-therapeutic-promise.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 23:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/senescence-in-cancer-hallmarks-paradoxes-and-therapeutic-promise</guid></item><item><title>Take-Two 似乎解雇了人工智能团队的部分人员，其中包括人工智能主管，具体人数不详。</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/take-two-has-seemingly-laid-off-an-unspecified-portion-of-its-ai-team-including-its-head-of-ai</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 12:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/take-two-has-seemingly-laid-off-an-unspecified-portion-of-its-ai-team-including-its-head-of-ai</guid></item></channel></rss>